{
  "texts": [
    "**Who**: Speakers, guests, men, women. 2.",
    "**What**: Smoking cigarettes and cigars. 3.",
    "**When**: During a talk, between the acts of a performance, after dinner, at social gatherings. 4.",
    "**Where**: Indoors (lobby, living room, table, designated smoking areas), outdoors (trains, planes, designated areas), restaurants, theaters, waiting rooms (with permission or designated areas), private rooms in hospitals, designated smoking sections in some venues. 5.",
    "**Why**: Smoking is seen as a personal preference, but consideration for others is important."
  ]
}